## Quick review of Markdown

I can make lists:
* thing 1
* thing 2
 
I can make ordered lists:
1. stuff 1
1. stuff 2

// note: no spaces in lists!

Blocks of code are useful sometimes:

```
I am 
a block 
of code
```

